{"tid":769980,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人都係咁？","createTime":"2018-08-06T15:34:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T15:36:41.000Z","uid":148087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e890098289b00c67a063ddb94bb4c8a97388ce52","tid":769980,"uid":148087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T15:34:44.000Z","msg":"睇住身邊啲中學同學係大學玩得好開心<br />\n就算佢都未知將來出社會做咩工 <br />\n最少佢地都讀緊u 都算係有個目標 知道自己做緊乜<br />\n但自己就戇鳩鳩咁 成廿幾歲人都未想自己想點<br />\n搵唔到一樣野係自己擅長 真係好似舊垃圾咁<br />\n但人地垃圾得嚟 係有家底 但自己垃圾得口嚟係乜都無<br />\n究竟可以點做？書又讀唔成 錢又無<br />\n樣靚既女仔都話可以搵老闆 再唔係就拍youtube <br />\n咁柒架呢？係咪可以去死？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每日都諗緊自己有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"314b629312a409b12099667cb5609de80295ae88","tid":769980,"uid":60552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T15:36:41.000Z","msg":"去搵嘢學囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講冇撚用嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}